@node Main "IconBar Help!"

	@{u}IconBar v2.0 © 1996 by Ben Matthew (a wacky, dacky type toolbar)@{uu}

	@{" Introduction   " link intro}  -  What is it and why the hell did I write it?
	@{" Features       " link features}  -  A quick rundown of stuff
	@{" Usage          " link use}  -  How it's all done + installation
	@{" Bugs/Comments  " link bugs}  -  I want your @{i}feedback@{ui}!
	
	@{" History        " link history}  -  These bugs are history now!

IconBar is a multi-purpose graphic toolbar which can generate images automatically from a set of pre-drawn files supplied by YOU (a demo internet icon "set" is supplied), - as many as you want - providing you want no more than 10!  It's also completely rescalable and has got a wonderful savable prefs!
	
@endnode

